  <!-- EN: Afterlife Vault -->
  <SoSAfterlifeVault.label>來世蒼穹</SoSAfterlifeVault.label>
  <!-- EN: Your colonists were among the millions who died during this rimworld's apocalyptic wars. As society collapsed around them, the extremely wealthy built "Afterlife Vaults" to house the brains of their deceased loved ones. Only a few were completed, and with the collapse of the global power grid their AIs generally decided to enter hibernation.\n\nNow, centuries later, the AI has concluded that rescue will never come. Your afterlife caskets are capable of generating formgels - swarms of mechanites which mimic the original bodies of the deceased - but power supplies only suffice to run one or two at a time.\n\nCan you secure a future for the long-dead? -->
  <SoSAfterlifeVault.description>你們幾人早已在曾經席捲整個邊緣世界的浩劫戰爭中死去。當社會秩序分崩離析時，那些巨企資本家們建造了「來世蒼穹」來存放已故親人的思維意識。由於項目受阻，真正完工的「來世蒼穹」只有寥寥幾艘。隨著全球電網的癱瘓，其搭載的AI決定進入休眠狀態。\n\n現在，幾個世紀的時光已悄然流逝，AI也因此得出了「被救援幾率為0%」的最終結論。你們構造艙上的擬形膠凝體裝置已被重新激活，但現有的電力供應也僅能維持一到兩個擬形膠凝體活動。\n\n你能帶給這些死去很久的人一個嶄新的未來嗎？</SoSAfterlifeVault.description>
  <!-- EN: Your colonists were among the millions who died during this rimworld's apocalyptic wars. As society collapsed around them, the extremely wealthy built "Afterlife Vaults" to house the brains of their deceased loved ones. Only a few were completed, and with the collapse of the global power grid their AIs generally decided to enter hibernation.\n\nNow, centuries later, the AI has concluded that rescue will never come. Your afterlife caskets are capable of generating formgels - swarms of mechanites which mimic the original bodies of the deceased - but power supplies only suffice to run one or two at a time.\n\nCan you secure a future for the long-dead? -->
