  <!-- EN: Afterlife Vault -->
  <SoSAfterlifeVault.scenario.name>來世蒼穹</SoSAfterlifeVault.scenario.name>
  <!-- EN: Some of you picked up a charge rifle and died for your country; others were ignominiously crushed under rubble when the first round of orbital bombings hit. In any case, you are all well and truly dead, casualties of this rimworld's apocalyptic wars.\n\nBefore society collapsed, your wealthy loved ones secured you a spot in one of the new "Afterlife Vaults," with the promise of your revived brain being able to interact with the world as a formgel - a swarm of mechanites which perfectly imitates your original body. And wouldn't you know it, the outlandish promises all turned out to be true.\n\nOf course, that was before the collapse of the global power grid. Over the centuries, the mechanoids guarding your tomb have one by one failed or been destroyed. The AI has finally calculated the odds of rescue to be negligible, and re-enabled your consciousnes.\n\nAt the moment, there is only enough power to run one or two formgels at a time. Can you build out power infrastructure and secure a future for the dead? -->
  <SoSAfterlifeVault.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>你們幾人早已在曾經席捲整個邊緣世界的浩劫戰爭中死去。當社會秩序分崩離析時，那些巨企資本家們建造了「來世蒼穹」來存放已故親人的思維意識。由於項目受阻，真正完工的「來世蒼穹」只有寥寥幾艘。隨著全球電網的癱瘓，其搭載的AI決定進入休眠狀態。\n\n現在，幾個世紀的時光已悄然流逝，AI也因此得出了「被救援幾率為0%」的最終結論。你們構造艙上的擬形膠凝體裝置已被重新激活，但現有的電力供應也僅能維持一到兩個擬形膠凝體活動。\n\n你能帶給這些死去很久的人一個嶄新的未來嗎？</SoSAfterlifeVault.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>
  <!-- EN: Six formgel colonists and a benevolent AI, but not enough power to run them all at once. -->
  <SoSAfterlifeVault.scenario.summary>六名擬形膠凝體殖民者和一個友好的AI，但你缺少足夠的能量來同時運行它們。</SoSAfterlifeVault.scenario.summary>
  
  <!-- EN: Derelict Ship -->
  <SoSDerelict.label>廢棄飛船</SoSDerelict.label>
  <!-- EN: The three of you awake in your cryptosleep sarcophagi, stirred from slumber by an automated warning. A storm of micrometeorites has torn several breaches in your ship's hull and destroyed its Johnson-Tanaka drive. Trapped in orbit above an unknown rimworld, you must patch up your damaged ship and make long-term survival plans. -->
  <SoSDerelict.description>你們三人在刺耳的警報聲與金屬碎裂聲中從休眠艙內醒來。一場微型隕石風暴撕裂了飛船的船體，並摧毀了約翰遜-田中驅動器。飛船被困在一個未知的邊緣世界的近地軌道上，你們必須想辦法修理好受損的飛船，並制定一份長期的生存計劃。</SoSDerelict.description>
  <!-- EN: The three of you awake in your cryptosleep sarcophagi, stirred from slumber by an automated warning. A storm of micrometeorites has torn several breaches in your ship's hull and destroyed its Johnson-Tanaka drive. Trapped in orbit above an unknown rimworld, you must patch up your damaged ship and make long-term survival plans. -->
  <SoSDerelict.scenario.description>你們三人在刺耳的警報聲與金屬碎裂聲中從休眠艙內醒來。一場微型隕石風暴撕裂了飛船的船體，並摧毀了約翰遜-田中驅動器。飛船被困在一個未知的邊緣世界的近地軌道上，你們必須想辦法修理好受損的飛船，並制定一份長期的生存計劃。</SoSDerelict.scenario.description>
  <!-- EN: Derelict Ship -->
  <SoSDerelict.scenario.name>廢棄飛船</SoSDerelict.scenario.name>
  <!-- EN: The three of you awake in your cryptosleep sarcophagi, stirred from slumber by an automated warning. A storm of micrometeorites has torn several breaches in your ship's hull and destroyed its Johnson-Tanaka drive. Trapped in orbit above an unknown rimworld, you must patch up your damaged ship and make long-term survival plans.\n\nPerhaps you can acquire resources by scanning for orbital sites. You could also turn your sensors towards the planet's surface to scout a potential landing site for your ship. -->
  <SoSDerelict.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>你們三人在刺耳的警報聲與金屬碎裂聲中從休眠艙內醒來。一場微型隕石風暴撕裂了飛船的船體，並摧毀了約翰遜-田中驅動器。飛船被困在一個未知的邊緣世界的近地軌道上，你們必須想辦法修理好受損的飛船，並制定一份長期的生存計劃。\n\n也許你可以通過掃瞄星球軌道來發現一些藏有資源的地點。你也可以將你的傳感器轉向星球表面，為你的飛船偵查潛在的著陸點。但無論如何，你都需要重新拾起所需的科技並妥善修理好飛船。</SoSDerelict.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>
  <!-- EN: Three survivors aboard a damaged starship. -->
  <SoSDerelict.scenario.summary>三名倖存者及一艘受損的飛船。</SoSDerelict.scenario.summary>
  
  <!-- EN: Space Station -->
  <SoSDungeon.label>廢棄空間站</SoSDungeon.label>
  <!-- EN: You left home to join a crew bound for the stars, signed up for a long-duration operation out on the Rim.\n\nAt least, that's what you thought you were getting into.\n\nUpon awakening in your cryptosleep casket to the sound of warning klaxons, you find yourself on a space station. Likely abandoned, the life support and artificial ecosystem have run amok, filling the habitation spheres with wild plant life. How long have you been buried in here? -->
  <SoSDungeon.description>你們三人離開家鄉加入了一支星際船隊，簽下了在邊緣世界長期工作的合同。\n\n至少你們認為是這樣的。\n\n在刺耳的警報聲中從休眠艙內醒來後，你們發現自己正處於一顆小行星的中心。依托其建造的空間站顯然早就被廢棄了。人工生態和生命維持系統已經失控，站內也被瘋狂生長的野生植物所佔據。你們到底被埋在這兒了多久了？</SoSDungeon.description>
  <!-- EN: You left home to join a crew bound for the stars, signed up for a long-duration operation out on the Rim.\n\nAt least, that's what you thought you were getting into.\n\nUpon awakening in your cryptosleep casket to the sound of warning klaxons, you find yourself on a space station. Likely abandoned, the life support and artificial ecosystem have run amok, filling the habitation spheres with wild plant life. How long have you been buried in here? -->
  <SoSDungeon.scenario.description>你們三人離開家鄉加入了一支星際船隊，簽下了在邊緣世界長期工作的合同。\n\n至少你們認為是這樣的。\n\n在刺耳的警報聲中從休眠艙內醒來後，你們發現自己正處於一顆小行星的中心。依托其建造的空間站顯然早就被廢棄了。人工生態和生命維持系統已經失控，站內也被瘋狂生長的野生植物所佔據。你們到底被埋在這兒了多久了？</SoSDungeon.scenario.description>
  <!-- EN: Space Station -->
  <SoSDungeon.scenario.name>廢棄空間站</SoSDungeon.scenario.name>
  <!-- EN: You left home to join a crew bound for the stars, signed up for a long-duration mining operation out on the Rim.\n\nAt least, that's what you thought you were getting into.\n\nUpon awakening in your cryptosleep casket to the sound of warning klaxons, you find yourself at the center of an asteroid. The mining base is abandoned. The life support and artificial ecosystem have run amok, filling the habitation spheres with wild plant life. How long have you been buried in here?\n\nThe power must have kicked back online after a tunnel collapse. One of the two reactors are down, the other is burning through the last of its fuel. With power dwindling, you might choose to put the remaining reactor into overdrive to ensure constant power. Or maybe try the backup chemfuel generators.\n\nThis far out on the Rim, rescue is unlikely. And you have a feeling you're not alone... -->
  <SoSDungeon.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>你們三人離開家鄉加入了一支星際船隊，簽下了在邊緣世界長期工作的合同。\n\n至少你們認為是這樣的。\n\n在刺耳的警報聲中從休眠艙內醒來後，你們發現自己正處於一顆小行星的中心。依托其建造的空間站顯然早就被廢棄了。人工生態和生命維持系統已經失控，站內也被瘋狂生長的野生植物所佔據。你們到底被埋在這兒了多久了？\n\n電力一定是在隧道坍塌後重新啟動的。兩個反應堆中的一個已經停擺了，另一個正在消耗僅剩的燃料。隨著電力的減少，你可能得讓剩下的那個反應堆超速運轉，以確保持續的電力。或者試試備用的化合燃料發電機。\n\n離邊緣世界這麼遠的地方是沒有救援的，而且這裡似乎不止有你們三人...</SoSDungeon.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>
  <!-- EN: Three survivors aboard a space station. -->
  <SoSDungeon.scenario.summary>三名倖存者及一個受損的小行星基地。</SoSDungeon.scenario.summary>
  
  <!-- EN: Load Ship -->
  <SoSLoadShip.label>載入飛船</SoSLoadShip.label>
  <!-- EN: Experimental feature - expect a ton of red and yellow alerts. These may or may not be harmless. If you encounter issues, give it a few second, then try loading and saving the game. If your ship didn't make it, we need your Player.log file in order to figure out what's going on!\n\nStart with a ship that has left for another planet. You can edit the scenario and select your saved ship bellow. You can also choose to discard logs and tales, lowering your save size. This will disable many other types of scenario part, such as starting pawns. -->
  <SoSLoadShip.description>注意：此劇本屬於實驗性功能，預計會產生大量紅黃字報錯。它們可能不會造成任何影響，當然也有可能...你懂的。\n如果你遇到了問題，可以先耐心等待一會，然後再試著載入和保存遊戲。如果你的飛船始終無法生成，請向SOS2的製作組反饋並提供完整的「Player.log」文件！\n\n此劇本將以前往另一個邊緣世界的飛船開始。你可以點擊下方的「劇本編輯器」按鈕來選擇先前保存的飛船。你還可以選擇刪掉已記錄的logs和tales來縮減存檔大小，但這樣做會禁用包括開局殖民者在內的許多劇本功能。</SoSLoadShip.description>
